om/zh-hant/</a><br />\n呢個網可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼漏了唔好意思！！<br />\nClick Compose 就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲可以去PROTON EMAIL<br />\n<a href=\"https://protonmail.com/signup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprotonmail.com%2Fsignup&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUysjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=dd680999\" target=\"_blank\">https://protonmail.com/signup</a>"},{"pid":"d6cecc54b4d708495a3855a981c12b11b842c57f","tid":1309421,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"The words of the people are written on the Lennon walls,<br />\nand Linden walls.<br />\n<br />\nIn restless dreams we work like teams,<br />\nmillions people may be more.<br />\n<br />\nAnd echoes in the world of freedom.<br />\n<br />\nI turn my wear to the dark and black.<br />\n<br />\nAnd the mission <br />\nthat was planted in my brain<br />\nStill remains."},{"pid":"c97bf590118ecba5e404c3f61c862bcbb73a44a2","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48374111f26b7c391cb2ffe9bbbf1cf3925b730a","tid":1309421,"uid":261166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"進入司法程序，唔識唔好亂黎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />脷伸：我唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"所以我地只可以提供證據<br />\n不要提及任何帶主觀色彩字眼 情緒字眼就最好"},{"pid":"e976c18aeead7efb017cc2b14eeeaba619dae8bd","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/625096/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/625096/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n做政府多年，發現識用正確方法，鬧政府、屌政府的香港人非常少 | LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n寫呢個post係想你，懂得如何正確地「屌政府」。<br />\n<br />\n1. 識上 Facebook、高登、香討、連登投訴政府的香港市民，多不勝數。<br />\n<br />\n但透過正常官方途徑，用email或寫信投訴的市民，很少。<br />\n<br />\n2. 好多人以為寫email俾政府冇用。但實際上 ，政府會搵個eo耍完你之後，會記錄在案，定期檢討。<br />\n<br />\n有需要的檢討完後會招標，搵外判商解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n3. 涉中共中央政府掌權的民生大事（即係真普選、內地移民問題），香港冇權話事。市民點遊行，佔中，點屌香港政府，都冇意義。唯有祈禱讓中共良心發現，或者頂唔順就移民。<br />\n<br />\n4. 不涉中共的民生大事（如樓價問題），但涉及各階層不同的利益，且高風險政策。基本要組織有100萬人先可以逼到政府 take action。<br />\n<br />\n講開遊行，主題最好要針對性（樓價問題就樓價問題）<br />\n<br />\n（一次的遊行，唔好又屌樓價高，又屌醫療差，又屌冇普選。屌太多野，唔集中主題，會好鬆散。成個遊行變左好似細路仔或港女哭鬧咁，變成冇意義的遊行）"},{"pid":"3e94b76cd6a70afa7cf0a3ddd0e2ca60b9f4d4a5","tid":1309421,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2de235014db3f9df073f72c81d725e965226d634","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a89c5bbdd94f58af9605b5d3b25ee0874e5ab78","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ycyN6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ycyN6Z.png&h=4ed023e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78775d2369951d185be00bcc63a9a33e35a7a11e","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c6ebe37fc53be67325628a9e3c6afc3f83ea8b","tid":1309421,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9d7efacd9111e25f727974de14b2e25f4f9eefd","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dc4db7d4da9f002a67e788924d91ef6d3485a5","tid":1309421,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f512258e62f8bb373d89e7fba8fca69f75fb35","tid":1309421,"uid":262340,